{"type":"message","id":"f65ce87e","parentId":"67979213","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:41:35.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经收集了四个行业的最新信息。让我整理3-5条关键信息摘要给用户。","thinkingSignature":"a1bffdc1a4ff2f5fb988e878f04918fc8b6b1cdb3756e8625daa5a27c681c889"},{"type":"text","text":"## 道简网络相关行业最新动态（2026年3月）- 关键信息摘要\n\n---\n\n### 1. 企业数字化转型：政策深化与规模化推进\n\n**北京市**提出2026年底实现规模以上制造业企业数字化转型达标，打造全国标杆。国家层面，工信部"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5492,"output":0,"cacheRead":30610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36102,"cost":{"input":0.0016476,"output":0,"cacheRead":0.0009182999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025659}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1773963684249,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}}
